high_descs: Go left and then left again to face the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick the soap up from the counter.
Go left and face the sink on the left.
Put the soap in the sink and turn the water on and then off and pick the soap up again.
Go right and then left to stand on the right side of the toilet, facing the toilet.
Put the soap on the back of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed bar of soap on the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn around, move to the right side of the sink.
Pick up the soap, right of the sink.
Bring the soap left to the left sink.
Wash the soap in the left sink.
Bring the washed soap over to the far side of the toilet on the right.
Put the soap on the toilet tank lid.
anns.task_desc: Put washed soap on the toilet tank lid.

high_descs: Turn left and hang a left at the white toilet to reach the right sink on the vanity.
Pick up the bar of soap to the right of the sink on the vanity.
Turn left and take a right at the wall to face the left sink of the vanity.
Put the bar of soap in the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn right, take a right around the toilet, turn left at the tub and face the toilet to the left at the wall.
Put the rinsed bar of soap on the right side of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed bar of soap on a toilet tank.
